page.title: 20Gt.Coxwell Acknowledgements
page.content: Many thanks are due to the following members of Great Coxwell Womens' Institute:- Ros Hall,Brenda Haskins and Pauline May. Also to non-members Ali Gould and Linz Best. A special thanks to Rosemary Church, the Secretary of the Faringdon and District Archaeological and Historical Society, who did the computing for us. Thanks also to Grange Infants School for lending the computer. I would also like to mention my late mother at whose bedside I wrote and rewrote much of my contribution. Catherine M.Gould October 1985
